When the angle of incidence of the electromagnetic waves increases, the wave travels a long geometric path through the gas layer57. Therefore, the interactions between the electromagnetic waves and gas molecules are improved. Hence, the sensitivity of the proposed structure is enhanced by increasing the incident angle. By increasing the incident angle from 0 to 45.30o (below \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
