Table 1 illustrates that the FoM of our sensor is 3.6×105 RIU and the QF is 4×103. The high value of the FoM indicates that the proposed sensor has high sensitivity and narrow FWHM simultaneously. In addition, the DL of the sensor is approximately 1.4×10−7 RIU, which indicates the smallest detectable refractive index change.Table 1
Different parameters of the proposed sensor at optimum conditions.
